title: Beautifully upgraded 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home
posting_body: ['Beautifully upgraded home in Renaissance community of Woodridge.', 'Private end unit with wonderful low maintenance patio, yard & deck.', ' Hardwood floors on the main, new paint throughout, newer travertine, stone, & ceramic tile floors in entry & both bathrooms.', 'Kitchen has newer stainless refrigerator & dishwasher.', 'Access from dining area to lovely deck & stairs to yard.', 'Large primary bedroom on upper level with big walk-in closet plus a spacious bathroom plus washer/dryer on upper level.', 'Lower level bedroom with own full bathroom.', 'Newer roof.', "Low HOA's.", 'No assessments.', 'Private location in complex.', 'A great opportunity to live, work, commute, shop & enjoy the access & conveniences of a fantastic location that is second to none.', 'Bellevue HS.', 'Email your number to set up a showing!']
